269
00:19:53.529 --> 00:19:56.108
<i>Serta buku-buku tua
tentang penyembuhan kuno.</i>


270
00:19:58.044 --> 00:20:00.288
<i>Ibuku selalu bilang...</i>

271
00:20:00.313 --> 00:20:03.044
<i>...Nenek semacam tabib
