00:24:45.044 --> 00:24:47.750
Hotel Grand Orleans Imperial Island,

360
00:24:47.802 --> 00:24:51.793
Menyambutmu dan rekan-rekan
kelompok dermawanmu.


361
00:24:51.842 --> 00:24:53.443
Aku hanya ingin bilang...

362
00:24:53.468 --> 00:25:00.886
